{"tid":126796,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[集思廣益]連登線上讀書會會員召募","createTime":"2017-02-19T15:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T04:59:48.000Z","uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"140046ac63626e564cc149ef1ead6ad356b0d40a","tid":126796,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:28:48.000Z","msg":"首先要向admin 表明呢個post 之所以唔開喺活動台係想召集更多有閱讀習慣嘅連登仔, 如admin認為應該轉去活動台, 小弟絕對ok<br />\n<br />\n其次係同各位巴絲道歉先, 本身話尋晚開post 衣加遲左24小時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然小弟參加過其他study group, 不過自己主持就未試過, 所以希望各位巴絲有怪莫怪<br />\n<br />\n最後多謝會然 22號寶寶 引左咁多有睇開書嘅連登仔上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢話少講, 入正題先(以下為書面語)<br />\n<br />\n1. 本讀書會目的: 豐富本讀書會會員的知識及提供ㄧ個互助平台予會員作學術交流<br />\n<br />\n2. 語音交流方式: Telegram/Skype/ RC<br />\n<br />\n3. 文件交流方式: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByBrU-tkwgGfcDQ0NHZrbi1DT2c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0ByBrU-tkwgGfcDQ0NHZrbi1DT2c&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=729029b4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByBrU-tkwgGfcDQ0NHZrbi1DT2c</a><br />\n歡迎各位把書評/ 讀書會交流書本之簡介等資訊上載至此平台<br />\n<br />\n4. 讀書會時間: 日期待定, 預計為定期線上聚會, 會長大約2-3小時並且接受早退/遲到. *注意*讀書會語音內容將被錄音並上載至上述雲端供其他會員聆聽<br />\n<br />\n5. 讀書會模式: 每次三至六人根據每次不同的題目介紹自己已完成閱讀之書籍, 時間視乎書種/題目而定<br />\n介紹方式請隨意<br />\n等每位講者介紹完畢後, 旁聽觀眾歡迎作出提問及加入討論<br />\n<br />\n6. 不會被討論之書籍種類: 待定<br />\n<br />\n7. 如何成為下次讀書會之講者: 於上述雲端名為[講者名單]的檔案內排期或於Telegram 私訊本人<br />\n<br />\n8. 有關讀書會詳細資訊之發佈方式: Telegram群組<br />\n<br />\n9. 加入方法: 於留言區留名並加入Telegram 群組<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEIAahoGlJRxmp1gDg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FAAAAAEIAahoGlJRxmp1gDg&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=d6b1ad57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/AAAAAEIAahoGlJRxmp1gDg</a><br />\n請於群組內簡單自我介紹以及說明自己感與不感興趣之書種<br />\n<br />\n10. 本人私下聯絡方法:<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/DrHedgehogLifePerDay\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FDrHedgehogLifePerDay&d=FGEw0iwwiNltpS2R1LMyGgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=79068559\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/DrHedgehogLifePerDay</a><br />\n(以上, 若有遺漏, 歡迎留言指出)<br />\n以下為口語<br />\n<br />\n根據Post [睇書撚]點解有咁多連登仔有睇書嘅習慣II, 小弟統計出大家最常睇/分享嘅五類書: <br />\n1. 華文文學類<br />\n2. 哲學類<br />\n3. 歷史類 (我將d關於地區古代飲食文化嘅書都歸入呢ㄧ類)<br />\n4. 日本文學類<br />\n5. 國外小說類<br />\n<br />\n暫時咁先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb8b3a1b933f108478c22188f4720a40e5e5f9f","tid":126796,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T15:35:19.000Z","msg":"利申: 個群組logo係網上歡迎下載嘅free logo尼, 絕非偷圖撚"},{"pid":"59022e48aad1af56a7d19dfb60cae883ced8a6fa","tid":126796,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:22:38.000Z","msg":"輕輕ㄧ推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d96c049742ccbdba0f04c1a1fea25c867cc1e3b6","tid":126796,"uid":5521,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申: 個群組logo係網上歡迎下載嘅free logo尼, 絕非偷圖撚</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">尼你老母臭閪</span></span><br />\n你讀乜撚嘢書啊<br />\n縮返入你老母個閪道讀屎片啦"},{"pid":"1e6e8dc7aeb4b55aa6fdc8c7778d4629443eda46","tid":126796,"uid":77205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:31:11.000Z","msg":"咪咁燥啦香港人"},{"pid":"c01aa8e71d726885715aa45689a7a724bf509555","tid":126796,"uid":49737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:45:29.000Z","msg":"你開嗰個好似係channel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"257e9cd0ab6c3712571baf9ab4e249077871339e","tid":126796,"uid":84924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T1